    <label>Cooltouch Z-Wave Switch 3-gang White</label>
    <description>Z-Wave Switch 3-gang White&lt;br /&gt&lt;h1&gtOverview&lt;/h1&gt&lt;p&gtCOOLTOUCH Z-Wave smart switch with touch panel. Curved touch buttons with glowing ring per button. Atmel MCU, Bayer case, Tyco relay, aluminium bezel.&lt;/p&gt &lt;p&gt&lt;strong&gtSpecification&lt;/strong&gt&lt;br /&gtStandard: Z-Wave Plus&lt;br /&gtVoltage: AC90~250V, 50/60Hz (Neutral &amp;amp; Live wire required)&lt;br /&gtLoad: resistive one of 500W, capacitive one of 200W&lt;br /&gtMaximum Current: 5A, impact resistance TV-5&lt;br /&gtRemote Distance: Indoor of 40m, outdoor of 80m&lt;br /&gtRemote Control Configuration: 0-close / 255-open&lt;br /&gtFrequency: 868.42MHz&lt;br /&gtCertification: CE, RoHS&lt;br /&gt&lt;br /&gtDimensions&lt;br /&gtSwitch Size: 86 x 86 x 38.6mm&lt;br /&gtDepth: 30mm&lt;/p&gt &lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtInclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;ul&gt&lt;li&gtTap any button on the switch, it lights up white.&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtPress and hold the same button until all buttons start glowing.&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtThen tap any button 3 times within 1 second.&lt;/li&gt &lt;/ul&gt&lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtExclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;ul&gt&lt;li&gtTap any button on the switch, it lights up white.&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtPress and hold the same button until all buttons start glowing.&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtThen tap any button 3 times within 1 second.&lt;/li&gt &lt;/ul&gt&lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtWakeup Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;p&gtThis is a mains powered unit, it is always awake.&lt;/p&gt</description>
